defaultADDITIONAL COMMENTSdefault&#xa0;defaultA LTC strategy needs to make clear links with 
defaulthelping people with LTCs retain and return to work. defaultThe link between health and work has been increasingly recognised, particularly since Dame Carol Black’s 2008 Review
default. 
defaultArthritis and related conditions are the second most common cause of days off work.
default With government funding, 
defaultArthritis Care has worked with stakeholders to produce an online work retention toolkit for people with long-term fluctuating conditions and their employers.
default The strategy could reference this resource, and seek to build on it.
